    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6">

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">How do I track my progress?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">You can create an account on Skill Maps to unlock progress tracking across all roadmaps.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">Are the learning pathways free?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Yes, all learning pathways and resources on Skill Maps are completely free and open to all learners.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">Can I suggest or contribute content?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Definitely! We're building a community of contributors. Reach out via the Contact page or join our Discord server to collaborate.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">Do I need an account to use Skill Maps?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">No account is required to view content. However, signing up unlocks progress tracking, notifications, and contributor tools.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">Are there certifications?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">We are currently working on a badge system and downloadable certificates upon completion of specific tracks. Stay tuned!</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">Is Skill Maps suitable for beginners?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Absolutely! Each roadmap is structured to support both newcomers and experienced developers, with clear progression and resources.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">Can I download or print a roadmap?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Yes. Each roadmap has a printable view and PDF download option under the roadmap settings menu.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">How often is the content updated?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">We regularly update our content every month, ensuring resources stay up-to-date with the tech industry.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">Who maintains Skill Maps?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Skill Maps is maintained by a team of software engineers, content writers, and educators. You can read more on our About page.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <summary class="text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer">How can I contact the team?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Visit the <a href="contact.html" class="text-green-700 hover:underline">Contact</a> page to get in touch with us or send suggestions directly.</p>
      </details>

    </div>

